I always ask that question of owners when they bring in an engine to
rebuild. What are you going to do with it? Dune buggies, airplane motor,
hovercraft? Then you can leave off a bunch of stuff. In your daily driver
that you don't want to rebuild real soon? Then leave all the factory stuff
on!

